Seeking revenge on his employer, a lazy bank agent and his two dim-witted friends concoct an elaborate but flawed heist.
A family’s festive Halloween plans take a spooky turn when an evil witch's curse transforms the costumed clan into actual monsters.
It's a new school year at Monster High, and the little sister of Clawdeen Wolf, Howleen, is determined to be more fangtastic than ever.

Titulo: Monster High: Boo York, Boo York
Enredo: Cleo is invited to a gala in the big city celebrating a magical comet and brings her best friends along. But the sinister Nefera has other plans.

Titulo: Monster High: Escape from Skull Shores
Enredo: A swanky cruise veers off course for Lagoona and her friends when they're left stranded on Skull Shores, an island with a notorious beast.
When Frankie Stein travels back in time, a teen scientist follows her home into the present and causes a lab accident that creates four new monsters.
In their bid to win the Skulltimate Roller Maze championship, Monster High loses its star players, Clawd and Deuce, to injury.
Big changes are afoot at Monster High when administrators announce a merger with two other schools, designed to bring all monsters together.
Draculaura is whisked to Transylvania to be crowned vampire queen, but when she learns she's been duped, the search is on for the true royal heir.
After learning that monsters and "Normies" used to spend Halloween together, Frankie Stein and her pals rally both groups for a frightfully good time.
At a Monster High party, Lagoona and pals are sucked into the reef, where she'll have to come to terms with her flaws and confront an old frenemy.
Hearing that their old school is being haunted, Spectra Vondergeist and her pals head back to Monster High to get to the bottom of the scary spookery.

Titulo: Monster High: New Ghoul at School
Enredo: Insecure new student Frankie Stein struggles to fit in at Monster High, where ultra-cool ghoul Cleo De Nile and hunky monster Deuce rule the roost.

Titulo: Monster High: Scaris, City of Frights
Enredo: When Clawdeen gets a chance to study with a top fashion designer, she and her pals hop on a plane to Scaris, France, the city where screams come true.

Titulo: Monster High: Why Do Ghouls Fall in Love?
Enredo: Draculaura's ghoulfriends have some suspicions about one of her two persistent suitors – but can they stop him before he steals her un-beating heart?
An office temp thinks she's found Mr. Right when she starts dating a handsome surgeon. But there's a problem standing in the way of everlasting bliss.
As he nears the end of a lonely three-year stint on the moon base Sarang, astronaut Sam Bell begins to hear and see strange things.
In a crime-infested Miami neighborhood, a gay African-American boy with a drug-addicted mother grows up with the help of a mentoring drug dealer.
A railway stationmaster tries to cope with his wife's death, his estrangement from his son and the corrupt world in which he lives.
When his father moves from the U.S. to Heidelberg, Germany, an African American teenager struggles to find his place and pursue his hip-hop dreams.
This comic documentary follows the Mortified movement, a series of stage events where adults share awkward childhood moments in front of strangers.
Two communities in Mumbai get a final chance to compete with each other in the celebration of the iconic Ganesh Chaturthi festival.
Motu and Patlu want to help a circus lion get back to the jungle. On the way, the three become caught up in an exciting adventure in the forest.
Featuring breathtaking imagery and thought-provoking narration, this film takes viewers to the summits of some of the world’s most amazing mountains.
An eye-popping cast stars in this sketch-comedy collage, the new millennium's homage to classic anthology films like The Kentucky Fried Movie.
After inheriting a media empire, humble Longfellow Deeds moves to the Big Apple – where a reporter and a company bigwig are waiting to pounce on him.

Titulo: Mr. Gaga: A True Story of Love and Dance
Enredo: World-renowned choreographer Ohad Naharin is profiled in this vivid documentary that mixes rehearsal footage with insights about his influence.
When a self-help author learns that his mother has fallen for his sadistic high school gym teacher, he tries to put a stop to their budding romance.
A successful advertising agency executive falls asleep on an airplane and wakes up in an alternate universe as a stay-at-home mom with three kids.
Two Mississippi teens meet peculiar drifter Mud and get caught up in his web of tall tales about lost love, crimes of passion and bounty hunters.
Samir must overcome a hostile horoscope, a hot temper and a determined rival to win the heart of Rani, the love of his life.
When the old guardian of the moon retires, the mischievous Mune is chosen as his successor, but he worries he's not up to the job.
A mild-mannered office drone plucks a Halloween party invitation off the street and suddenly finds himself the main event at a "murder party."
Marlon Brando gives a nuanced performance as the aristocratic Lt. Fletcher Christian, an officer aboard the HMS Bounty who leads a mutiny against the ship's tyrannical Capt. Bligh.

Titulo: My Babysitter's a Vampire: The Movie
Enredo: When their parents head out for the evening, Ethan and his little sister get the babysitter of their nightmares: a fledgling vampire named Sarah.
After being diagnosed HIV-positive, a champion swimmer is disowned and harassed by all except his loving sister and loyal boyfriend.
After the sudden loss of her husband, a mother has a crisis of faith and struggles to keep her life together for the sake of her daughter and herself.
Relocated to a new post and struggling to adjust, a police officer further complicates his life by falling for a woman he has little in common with.

Titulo: My Entire High School Sinking Into the Sea
Enredo: After an earthquake sends their school building drifting into the sea, a group of high-schoolers struggles to survive and overcome clique wars.
A recently dumped attorney hires a psychic to help her win back her boyfriend. Things take an unexpected turn when another ex re-enters the picture.
Amid the chaos and horror of World War II, a committed German soldier fights a private battle with his own conscience.
A 9-year-old boy finds his life upended when he's sent to live in an orphanage in this stop-motion animated tale of loss, friendship and young love.

Titulo: My Little Pony Equestria Girls: Friendship Games
Enredo: Rainbow Dash, Applejack and friends compete against Crystal Prep Academy and their lead athlete, this world's Twilight Sparkle, in sporting events.

Titulo: My Little Pony Equestria Girls: Rainbow Rocks
Enredo: Rainbow Dash, Applejack, Pinkie Pie, Rarity and Fluttershy plan to perform with their new band at the Canterlot High musical showcase.
After the untimely demise of her first three husbands, a stoic single mom is left to raise twelve children on her own and provide for her big family.
After speaking with former Scientology members and being stonewalled by higher-ups, filmmaker Louis Theroux hires actors to re-create alleged events.
A former defense attorney finds herself back in court when she and her husband are sued for medical emancipation by their 11-year-old daughter.
A bullied student forms a bond with the leader of a youth gang and discovers the power and meaning of true friendship.
While filming a movie in England, Hollywood icon Marilyn Monroe slips away with a young Brit for a week of self-discovery and frivolity.
A man finds his marriage to a dedicated women's rights activist facing some unexpected challenges over her commitment to the cause.
After losing her father, a young woman moves to the city to earn money. When she finds a job at a mysterious bungalow, her worst nightmares come true.
This documentary examines the naked yoga gurus of India whose devout spiritual practice connects them to the eternal, transcending the material world.
Recently paralyzed in a devastating car accident, Dana begins to suspect a dark and sinister force may be lurking within her hospital room.
Scientists and animal keepers fight to save an orphaned baby elephant at a rescue camp in Botswana while struggling to defend its entire species.
While loyally defending his boss from mobsters trying to kill him, a naive, hotel bellboy discovers the family he never knew he had.
Aimless valet driver Steven Bassem can't find the motivation to get a better job, even when his fractious immigrant family starts falling apart.
Mistakenly accused of an attack on the Fourth Raikage, ninja Naruto is imprisoned in the impenetrable Hozuki Castle and his powers are sealed.
Chile's Natalia Valdebenito hits Santiago's Teatro Caupolicán with a one-woman show steeped in irony, a dash of improv and her own personal style.
Three former military operatives offer disturbing, firsthand accounts of the deadly impact that U.S. drone warfare has had on civilians overseas.

In this parody of the Lethal Weapon franchise, criminals murder a detective and steal her prized evidence: microfilm with a recipe for cocaine cookies. Luckily, loose-cannon cop Jack Colt and his by-the-book partner, Wes Luger, are on the case.
Narrated by Robert Redford, this documentary tours the awe-inspiring landscapes, historic sites and untamed wilderness of America's great parks.
Modern treasure hunters search for a chest of riches rumored to have been stashed away by George Washington, Thomas Jefferson and Benjamin Franklin.
A veteran Shakespearean actor steps off the stage and into the painful tragedy of old age, facing ungrateful family and his fleeting legacy.
The biggest pranksters on YouTube – VitalyzdTV, Dennis Roady and Roman Atwood – turn Hollywood into "Prankwood" with their most over-the-top stunts.
As the new kid, a shy high school senior finds himself tormented by all his peers except one. But his new friend has a dark, infectious outlook.
Sir David Attenborough examines a recently discovered collection of dinosaur fossils. CGI and 3-D scans reveal what the beast may have looked like.
Shocking footage shows Nazi concentration camps after liberation, including Buchenwald and Ohrdruf, where Gen. Eisenhower ordered local Nazis to tour.
When a Chilean policeman vows to find and capture leftist poet Pablo Neruda, a game of cat and mouse ensues that tests both their wills.
As his father sits behind bars, a young man is lured into Los Angeles' merciless drug world and forced to choose between God and gang life.
When bickering teenage twins accidentally land in the middle of a criminal operation, they'll have to work together to get themselves out of trouble.
This intimate portrait sheds light on the trauma experienced and strength displayed by those affected by the 2012 massacre in Newtown, Connecticut.
Las Vegas magician Cris can see a few minutes into the future and an FBI agent wants his help thwarting a nuclear attack.
With numbers written on a doll as their only clue, three officers of the law track down a psychotic killer, unearthing dark secrets along the way.
A pair of young environmentalists enlist the help of an ex-military explosives expert to carry out a dangerous act of eco-terrorism.
After a prank goes sideways, three buddies find their relationships  – with women and each other – tested in unexpected ways.
A woman enters a quirky mental health clinic after attempting suicide upon finding out her husband is having an affair with her best friend.
Kate, an uptight chef, finds her life turned upside down when her sister dies in a car accident and she becomes her niece's sole guardian.

Titulo: Norm of the North: Family Vacation
Enredo: Stressed by his duties as king and father, Norm must secretly find his stolen crown while taking his family on a much-needed vacation.

Titulo: Norm of the North: Keys to the Kingdom
Enredo: When Norm the polar bear is framed for a crime he didn’t commit, his friends step up to help him clear his name.
An 18-year-old struggling to understand her best friend's suicide talks to teenagers who have grappled with mental illness and suicidal thoughts.
Scientists test avian aptitude and challenge concepts of intelligence with examples ranging from puzzle-solving crows to parrots with a sense of time.
Astrophysicists show how black holes might hold answers to how the universe evolved, leading to life on Earth and, ultimately, the human race.
Thirty years after Chernobyl’s nuclear disaster, engineers race against time to complete a new dome to contain the reactor’s lethal radiation.
The chariot dominated Chinese warfare for millennia. Now, a team of experts is building their own and unlocking its many secrets.
Drilling into the impact crater of the asteroid that wiped out the dinosaurs, a group of scientists unearths new evidence about the catastrophic event.
After decades of amazing discoveries, spacecraft Cassini embarks on its final – and most daring – mission: a dive below Saturn’s rings.
Scientists investigate Earth’s climate machine, looking for clues across the globe, from Greenland’s ice sheet to the desert of Australia.
Scientists reveal how the 2017 solar eclipse provided new clues into how the sun works, from its scorching atmosphere to its deadly solar storms.
From huge tusks to giant horns, some animals sport weaponry that’s larger than life. Researchers explain the science behind this biological arms race.
During risky expeditions in an underwater cave, scientists unearth a 13,000-year-old skeleton to gain insight into the earliest known humans in America.
At a former Nazi execution site in Lithuania, an international team of archaeologists searches for a lost escape tunnel dug by Jewish prisoners.
Scientists search for evidence left behind by the world’s greatest floods and predict if climate change will cause even greater aquatic disasters.
Scientists research the world’s deadliest hurricane, trying to understand what this 18th-century storm could tell us about our own future.
Evidence of a mysterious medieval famine leads researchers on a quest for one of the deadliest volcanoes in human history.
This documentary details how the water disaster in Flint, Michigan happened, its lasting effects, and the lengthy efforts it took to correct it.
With the science of forecasting flourishing, this documentary explores how predictions inform our lives and statistics and algorithms' reliability.

Titulo: NOVA: Secrets of the Shining Knight
Enredo: A master armorer and his team recreate parts of a knight's medieval armor and test its strength while rediscovering centuries-old metalworking secrets.
An international team of rescue workers race to save 12 young soccer players and their coach trapped in a flooded cave in Thailand.
Two adventurous pilots attempt to fly around the world without using any fuel, relying only on the power of the sun.
With access to the scientists and engineers responsible for the Curiosity rover's on-the-ground experiments, NOVA captures its landing on Mars.
Dissatisfied with the police’s progress, a teen and his best friend investigate their classmate's murder, treading down a dark path to the uneasy truth.
Waxing nostalgic about the bittersweet passage from childhood to puberty, four childhood girlfriends recall the magical summer of 1970.

Titulo: Now More Than Ever: The History of Chicago
Enredo: This rockumentary tells the behind-the-scenes story of the Hall-of-Fame band Chicago, from their jazz-rock fusion roots to chart-topping pop hits.
Raised by his aunt since he was a young boy, charismatic John Lennon is suddenly reunited with his mother, Julia, which ignites a bitter battle.
Guided by survivors' testimonies, this documentary explores the history and meaning of the numbers tattooed on the bodies of Auschwitz prisoners.

Titulo: Numero Zero. The Roots of Italian Rap
Enredo: In the '90s, the explosive popularity of hip-hop music in Italy impacts the nation's character while creating a new kind of renegade artist.
A self-diagnosed nymphomaniac reveals a lifetime of sexual experiences to a man who saves her from being beaten in an alley.
The second half of Lars von Trier's epic follows Joe as her reignited sex addiction destroys her family and thrusts her toward a surprising new trade.
This film details the rise of British rock group Oasis and the creativity and chaos that brothers Noel and Liam Gallagher brought to the iconic band.
After being fired from her job and dumped by her cheating boyfriend, a comedian has a one-night stand. Weeks later, she finds out she's pregnant.
This documentary examines the vital role water plays in human existence and the cause-and-effect interplay between oceans and the environment.
When aliens take over their small Australian town, a modest group of survivors must unite to fend off their otherworldly intruders.
Frank Sinatra leads an all-star cast as Danny Ocean, who decides to knock over a few casinos on the Las Vegas Strip with his buddies.
This entry in the all-star caper franchise finds debonair con man Danny Ocean and his gang taking revenge on a double-crossing Las Vegas kingpin.
Danny Ocean reunites with his old flame and the rest of his merry band of thieves in a caper covering three huge heists in Rome, Paris and Amsterdam.
Fallen Los Angeles police officer Terrence Downe finds new life as a secret weapon: a scientifically altered super-cop with unlimited lives.
The spirited trio are back to take on a new ghost-busting adventure at a mens' residence, where spooky secrets lurk around every corner.
After a body is discovered in their building, a vengeful, paranormal presence begins to affect Taew, Mod Dum and Cartoon's business.
Ghosts wreak havoc at the old school, and a student communicates with the spirit while the team reckons with a power struggle.
Domestic terrorist Timothy McVeigh's bomb attack on an Oklahoma City federal building in 1995 is chronicled in this examination of the shocking event.
In this second sequel of the trilogy, marital strife brews as Omar pursues a music career despite Salma’s wishes that he opt for a more stable job.
Two rebellious, hot-headed teenage brothers get caught up in gang life, which has dangerous repercussions for their family and friends.

Titulo: On Yoga The Architecture of Peace
Enredo: Based on photographer Michael O’Neill’s book of the same name, this documentary traces the author’s 10-year journey through the landscape of yoga.
Seeking to heal after a traumatic assault, a young woman retreats to a small village by the hills, where she finds hope, love and new purpose.

Titulo: Once In A Lifetime Sessions with Moby
Enredo: Through performances and interviews, musician Moby opens up about his unusual childhood, his heroes and the stories behind his songs.
Award-winning documentarian Morgan Spurlock turns his camera on boy band phenomenon One Direction in this combination concert film and backstage pass.

Titulo: One Heart: The A.R. Rahman Concert Film
Enredo: In this concert film, Indian musical maestro A.R. Rahman performs 15 of his most popular songs and reveals himself through interviews and clips.
After 25 years of searching, a lonely dentist finds his long-lost daughter but learns that she suffers from a rare medical condition.
Infertility affects millions. One couple copes with the assisted reproduction process by documenting its pain, disappointment and potential joy.
An obsession with a woman with whom he had a one-night stand brings disharmony into a man's life and destroys his peace of mind.
When a cop kills the brother of an expat American gangster who runs a Bangkok fight club, his crime-boss mother flies in to supervise revenge.
Given unprecedented access to soldiers and terrorists alike, journalist Michael Ware presents an epic, uncensored, intimate account of the Iraq War.
To pave the way for a major amphibious invasion, a team of South Korean spies goes behind enemy lines to steal a map of North Korean coastal defenses.
In a dangerous area of the Mekong River, a drug raid ending in 13 deaths arouses the suspicions of a narcotics officer who sets out to find the truth.
A Russian mobster, a Cuban spy and a smooth operator from Miami scheme to sell a Soviet submarine to a Colombian drug cartel for $35 million.
A special task force takes on a risky operation to evacuate civilians amid civil war. Based on the 2015 mission to rescue Chinese citizens in Yemen.
When the village's biryani cook unexpectedly passes, a widow steps up to the plate and takes on new delectable challenges.
Young orphan Kuttappayi goes to live with his grandfather in the country, but his new life takes a hard turn when his grandfather's health fails.
A young man invents a device he hopes will generate wireless energy, but instead, it proves to spark sinister, supernatural activity in his home.
In a battle of the bands, a percussions student and her musical kindred spirits set out to prove the merits of Chinese folk against the Western canon.
After a failed mission, an ex-Royal Marines Commando tries to overcome his demons while investigating the death of his ex-girlfriend's father.
An orphan girl taught magic by her sick grandma must find work in seedy Bangkok, where unsavory characters run afoul of her increasingly dark powers.
A prostitute who is down on her luck gets caught in the middle of an elaborate scheme orchestrated by two local politicians.
When she loses her beloved husband to a brain tumor, grieving widow Holly Kennedy learns that he left a series of letters behind to help her cope.
A face painter for Theyyam rituals who is himself disfigured conceals his guilt over the fact that he performs abortions as a medical practitioner.
This documentary traces the steps of druglord Pablo Escobar with vivid eyewitness accounts that reconstruct his bloody reign in Colombia.
When profit-seekers threaten to take over a bar in a tourist town, local martial artists put their skills to the test and fight back.
This fictionalized account of three real-life notorious Harlem drug dealers is told in flashbacks as they plunge into the world of hustling.
In the wake of a young artist’s suicide, his pianist mother and his despairing girlfriend square off in a living nightmare beset by guilt and blame.
In this documentary, a centuries-old horse race in the city of Siena, Italy, is the forum for a showdown between a young jockey and his former mentor.
Finding a tantalizing clue in an old letter, a young woman journeys to her family's tropical plantation to uncover generations of secrets.
A woman and her daughter are caught in a game of cat-and-mouse with burglars in their New York City home and are forced to retreat inside a vault.
After witnessing a murder, a meek family man must summon his courage when he finds himself on the wrong side of a notorious gangster.
A young newlywed tries to keep her relationship afloat after developing feelings for her older, TV writer boss.
When Katie and Micah fear their home may be haunted by a demonic presence, Micah sets up a video camera to document all the action.
Prompted by loyalty, Arjun plays matchmaker between his philandering foster brother and a conservative girl but winds up falling in love himself.
As the parents of three unmarried daughters, a humble cook and his wife contend with the challenges of matchmaking and social expectations.
This Sundance prize-winning documentary is an intimate portrait of 1980s Harlem drag balls: a world of fierce competition, sustenance, and survival.
Air marshal John Cutter must stop notorious terrorist Charles Rane from killing hostages on board a flight that should have delivered Rane to jail.
A talented young Indian cricket player must defy his father's wishes to play for the side of England, a rebellion his siblings quietly cheer.
A surgeon claims to remove high tech microchips that aliens used to manipulate the human race. This documentary seeks to separate fact from fiction.
CIA desk jockey Jack Ryan plunges into the heart of international terrorism after spoiling an assassination attempt on a British royal family member.
Sent to a remote village to write a screenplay, Sinan finds inspiration to spare in colorful locals, farcical misadventures and the craziness of love.
An overzealous security guard finds himself in over his head when he tries to thwart a criminal mastermind's plot to rob an entire shopping mall.
A wealthy businessman's miserly habits cause no small amount of stress and embarrassment to his family, particularly his daughter.
Desperate for a place to live, twentysomething bachelors Parikshit, Jayesh, Parag and Bhavesh finally locate a house to rent, only to learn that the landlords will consider married applicants only.
Mak's friends just want to protect him, but his wife Nak won't let a small thing like her own death get in the way of true love in this horror-comedy.
Amid an avalanche of stars, Pee-wee straps on his ice skates and glides into the holiday season with Christmas cards, carols ... and Charo.
In this modern fairy tale, a young woman cursed with the nose of a pig lives her life in seclusion – until an unlikely beau stumbles onto the scene.
The lives of several friends are thrown into chaos when a woman becomes pregnant by her husband's gay best friend after a drunken one-night stand.

Titulo: Perfect Bid: The Contestant Who Knew Too Much
Enredo: A "Price Is Right" superfan brings a bit of scandal to the long-running show by figuring out the answers to the questions before they're asked.
Ro risks her life to discover the identity of a stranger lurking on the Internet who might hold the answers to her friend's murder.
A psychic medium takes a job as personal shopper for a spoiled celebrity in order to contact the spirit of her brother, who owned her employer's home.
His hilltop farm in Vermont may be bucolic, but making ends meet is a backbreaking challenge for grizzled, hard-drinking organic farmer Peter Dunning.
In this mix of live action and CGI, rascally Peter Rabbit faces a tough new foe in his ongoing battle for the veggies in Mr. McGregor's garden.
India's highlands descend into bullet-riddled mayhem as the longtime rivalries and ruthless revenge missions among four men come to a head.
A boy whose illness allows him to float outside his body uses his newfound skill to help a cop take on a madman who's terrorizing New York City.
The paths of a man and a woman, who have both been recently divorced from their spouses, intersect at an art exhibition in London.
Struck by the lack of clean resources for menstruating women in his village, a jobless loafer braves social stigmas to create low-cost sanitary napkins.
Five Labrador puppies embark on a 20-month training to pass the milestones on their journey to becoming guide dogs for people with visual impairment.
In the midst of ann arduous divorce battle, a real estate tycoon opts for a life of partying and sex until feelings for his childhood friend surface.
As a lonely widower prepares to leave India to live with his children in America, he looks back on past memories and unfinished business.
Thakur Avadh is an evil landlord in a remote village who rules with an iron fist. His two sons live a debauched life, knowing that their father will bail them out of any scrape.
A group of hardscrabble young thieves in Argentina decide to leave their boss and plan heists on their own.
When a Paris-based writer with AIDS meets a college student exploring his sexuality, romance blossoms in his waning days.
When Earth's superheroes exile the volatile Incredible Hulk to a distant planet called Sakaar, the muscle-bound green monster is sold into slavery.
In pre-World War II France, two sisters purport to be able to communicate with the dead and soon catch the eye of an ambitious filmmaker.
A soldier grows disillusioned as he's caught between rival sergeants in this semi-autobiographical Vietnam War drama from writer-director Oliver Stone.
Captured by Nazis and sent to Auschwitz, a Jewish musician is assigned to soothe other prisoners marching to their deaths in the gas chambers.
Step inside the Ubisoft offices, and follow designer Jason VandenBerghe's fight to create the video game "For Honor" over four years.

Titulo: Pope Francis: A Man of His Word
Enredo: Documentary filmmaker Wim Wenders travels the world with Pope Francis, recording the controversial pontiff's humanist views in a sharply divided age.
During a storm that wrecks his ship, super-strong sailor Popeye washes ashore and winds up rooming at the Oyl household, where he meets Olive.
In a coastal Portuguese city, an erotic encounter ensues between an American expat and a French student, resonating through their lives years later.
After being recruited to be a raconteur in London, a handsome teenager discovers he suffers from a rare condition where he faints upon seeing fine art.

Titulo: Power Rangers Samurai: Christmas Together, Friends Forever (Christmas Special)
Enredo: On Christmas Eve, as the teens at Shiba House reflect on their first year together, they get an unexpected lesson on the true spirit of the holidays.

Titulo: Power Rangers Samurai: Clash of the Red Rangers
Enredo: The Samurai Rangers team up with the RPM Ranger Red to fight off Master Xandred's Mooger army and a robotic villain from the RPM Ranger's dimension.

Titulo: Power Rangers Samurai: Party Monsters (Halloween Special)
Enredo: On Halloween night, the creepiest creatures from the Netherworld trade war stories about their battles with the Samurai Power Rangers.

Titulo: Power Rangers Super Megaforce: The Legendary Battle (Extended)
Enredo: New footage augments the tale of the Rangers, who give their all to save Earth from Vrak and Emperor Mavro, as the Armada stages an epic final attack.

Titulo: Power Rangers Super Samurai: Stuck on Christmas
Enredo: The Samurai Rangers get stuck in the Megazord's cockpit on Christmas Eve when it breaks down. Can the Rangers get out in time for Christmas?

Titulo: Power Rangers Super Samurai: Trickster Treat
Enredo: When a Nighlok invades the Samurai Rangers' dreams and turns them into nightmares, the Rangers must figure out what is reality and what is illusion.
On Halloween, the scariest night of the year, the Rangers have a strange encounter with a mysterious medium who conjures "visions" of monsters past.

Titulo: Power Rangers: Megaforce: The Robo Knight Before Christmas
Enredo: Robo Knight learns the meaning of Christmas from a group of children when he is mistaken for a donated Christmas toy and is shipped to a foreign land.
The chaotic ramblings of a young architect's mind take hold of his life as he leaves behind his past in India to work in Prague.
Frank Capra's documentary chronicles the rise of authoritarianism in Germany, Italy and Japan as America prepares for a defense of liberty.
A man and a woman struggling to keep their respective marriages afloat run into each other at a marriage counselor's office, with unexpected results.
A documentarian uses his own family's experiences as a springboard to explore the ethical issues surrounding the FDA and pharmaceutical industry.
When a blood-spattered altar boy is found running from a murder scene, his conviction seems certain – but his attorney is determined to win the case.
When a confident college professor is courted by four eligible and well-established men, she struggles to decide who she likes the best.

Titulo: Prosecuting Evil: The Extraordinary World of Ben Ferencz
Enredo: A gripping profile of Ben Ferencz, the last surviving lead prosecutor at the Nuremberg trials whose lifelong desire for justice altered the rule of law.
A notorious terrorist manipulates an Indian army major's jilted lover into helping him obtain a classified military code.
This stylized crime caper weaves together stories featuring a burger-loving hit man, his philosophical partner and a washed-up boxer.
During a time of political turmoil, a mother goes on a journey in search of her missing son, who has been misjudged and labeled a terrorist.
In this remake of a 1996 Danish thriller, a drug pusher incurs his suppliers' wrath when he gets busted and is left without the money he owes.
Matters of the heart introduce chaos into the once-idyllic bachelor existence of three young men who share an apartment.
At San Quentin State Prison, hardened convicts take their shots at redemption while navigating personal struggles by bonding through basketball.
Driven beyond the bounds of convention, adventurer Gertrude Bell leaves turn-of-the-century Britain behind for the deserts of the Middle East.
After discovering a pair of young ghosts, a nebbish 11-year-old agrees to help the sibling spirits solve the mystery surrounding their demise.
Longstanding family conflicts resurface when a former model who's been in and out of rehab for a decade returns home for her sister's wedding.

Titulo: Radical: the Controversial Saga of Dada Figueiredo
Enredo: This film chronicles the career of surfer Dadá Figueiredo, whose stormy personal life upended his status as a trendsetting '70s sports hero.
An elderly, hearing-impaired Indian man stays connected to the world of the past through the beloved valve radio he has owned since childhood.
This gritty biopic of brutal boxer Jake LaMotta portrays a tormented soul rising to the top of his sport, only to be undone by his demons.
The murder of a teenage girl found dead in her bedroom opens up a twisted investigation that leads into a dark, murky labyrinth of secrets and lies.

Titulo: Raiders!: The Story of the Greatest Fan Film Ever Made
Enredo: Three childhood friends attempt to finish the pet project they've worked on for over 30 years: re-creating "Raiders of the Lost Ark" shot for shot.
During World War II, a Chinese railroad worker leads a group of brave resistance fighters against the forces of Japanese occupation.
A grad student leaves her boyfriend in Delhi for a job interview in Mumbai, where she reconnects with an old flame for whom she still has feelings.

Titulo: Ralph Breaks the Internet: Wreck-It Ralph 2
Enredo: When video-game bad guy Ralph and best friend Vanellope discover a way onto the internet, they set off on a mission to save her broken game.
Abandoned by her new husband and father of her son, a mountain woman journeys to Calcutta to find him, constantly tested by social evils along the way.
Ramen chef Masato travels to Singapore to retrace his mother's life and finds a deeper understanding of his family history and culture.
A small-town cook moves to London to earn a living, but from his employer’s sudden death to the immigration officials on his trail, plans soon go sour.
When Prince Lee Cheong returns to Joseon after his brother’s death, he finds the kingdom plagued by deadly creatures – but they’re not the only threat.
Believing himself to be God's envoy, a troubled young man embarks on a killing spree as his passion for music becomes a psychotic obsession.
Explore the icky world of rats and witness how their talent for surviving in almost any environment has led to catastrophic events throughout history.
When a series of seemingly random people are murdered, baffled police search for a killer who may have a connection to them all.
Bollywood superstar Salman Khan plays Prem, an heir to a perfume fortune who falls in love with the wrong woman in this romantic comedy.
When Jim Stark arrives in a new town with his troubled past firmly in tow, he quickly falls for the girl next door and befriends the vulnerable Plato.
Struggling to move on from a heartbreaking loss, Mikey is drawn into a dangerous underworld robbery orchestrated by his unreliable stepbrother Dale.
A family Christmas gathering at an isolated Australian estate turns into the holiday from hell after a mysterious stranger turns up at the door.
A group of teenagers witnesses Soviet and Cuban paratroopers descending on their small Colorado town and systematically setting off World War III.
When a theater group stages a production of a Rabindranath Tagore play, they begin to notice parallels between the story and their own lives.
A documentarian details her Jewish family's escape from Nazi-occupied Prague to refuge in Brazil, where her father built a life as an architect.
Five acclaimed photographers travel the world to provide detailed insight into the difficult conditions faced by refugees who dream of a better life.
Inside one of Cairo's most impoverished areas exists a place where criminals control everything and everyone.
Vice magazine's Andy Capper follows rapper Snoop Dogg on a pilgrimage to Jamaica, where he rechristens himself Snoop Lion, a reggae artist.
Following the written instructions of his friend, senile Zev crosses the country to find and murder the Nazi who killed their families in Auschwitz.
A psychologist is murdered after unveiling a breakthrough invention that extracts memories, spurring a fixated former patient to hunt for answers.
The results of a DNA test spur Puerto Rican rap icon Residente to set out on a global voyage in search of his roots and fresh musical inspiration.
After 30 years with the New York City Ballet, celebrated dancer Wendy Whelan redefines herself as an artist in a new stage of life.
When thugs prey upon innocent factory workers, a small-time scammer trains for revenge by studying the moves of Shaolin temple monks.
After four years together, a husband and wife become entangled in secret, sexually charged relationships that threaten to unravel their marriage.
In gritty 1980s New York, two Chinese immigrant boys rise through the ranks of the infamous Green Dragons gang, where they're trained to kill.
Gorgeous and free-spirited Albanian model Rezeta arrives in Mexico City, and soon uses her charms to take up a carefree new life in the metropolis.
Two detectives investigate a rash of vigilante killings linked to an old case, suggesting they might have put an innocent man behind bars.
Desperate to save his land, an indebted farmer journeys to Pandharpur to seek divine blessing with his small son, who searches for his mother.
A heartbroken wildlife photographer throws himself into his work, only to find himself experiencing strange transformations.
In a village where girls are auctioned off rather than married, a man falls in love with a girl who is about to face the bidders.
As communal violence erupts in his neighborhood, a Muslim mechanic presses forward to repair a historic truck that will transport Gandhi’s last remains.
Their marriage failing, Victoria and Izu try to reconnect during a road trip. But bringing long-repressed secrets to light threatens yet more discord.

Titulo: Roberto Saviano: Writing Under Police Protection
Enredo: Italian TV host Pif revisits Roberto Saviano, who's been living under protection since publishing "Gomorrah," his exposé on organized crime in Naples.
When the Sheriff of Nottingham takes his beloved captive, Robin Hood embarks on a daring rescue mission at the tyrant's castle.
Sylvester Stallone shot to fame as Rocky Balboa, an unknown fighter who's given a shot at fighting world champ Apollo Creed as a publicity stunt.
Featuring a rousing climax, this engaging sequel finds boxer Rocky Balboa returning to the ring for a rematch against reigning champ Apollo Creed.
After taking a pounding from a powerful young fighter, humbled world champ Rocky Balboa turns to ex-rival Apollo Creed for help in regaining his form.
Rocky Balboa takes on the Cold War, coming out of retirement to battle a Soviet fighter who pulverized Rocky's friend and former rival, Apollo Creed.
Inspired by the memory of his trainer, a broke and seemingly careerless Rocky finds glory in training and takes on an up-and-coming boxer.
In this dystopian sequel, kills equal points in a violently gory annual cross-country road race sponsored by the United Corporations of America.
Hoping to earn money to support her son, a single mother sings in a nightclub, where danger lurks around every corner.
This compelling documentary follows the 2012 Steubenville, Ohio rape case, putting social media and high school football culture in the spotlight.
As the newspaper industry takes a hit, The Denver Post breaks new ground with a section dedicated to cannabis culture.
Kidnapped, confined to a tiny room and raped, a young woman gives birth to a son. When he reaches his fifth birthday, she begins plotting an escape.
To save his parents’ home, a lottery-squandering 32-year-old man sublets a room to a disarmingly creepy tenant.
A gentle witch with a ginger braid offers rides to a variety of animals on her increasingly crowded broom, much to her grumpy cat's chagrin.
This documentary explores the rich heritage of Indian classical music and the reasons behind its modern decline in popularity.
A woman is thrilled to find out she's pregnant. But as her belly grows, the more certain she becomes that her unborn child is in serious danger.
A law student befriends and "befoes" a fellow gambling addict and a club owner, and tensions run high when they must come up with $15k in just 5 days.
Following the untimely death of his father, a young man begins to reconnect with his family while uncovering some difficult truths.
An ex-MMA champion reduced to fixing fights in Mexico must win one last match to save his girlfriend, who's been kidnapped by the mob.
During a visit to the Bronx to help out at his uncle's store, a cheerful martial arts expert springs into action when a gang terrorizes the shop.
When Sarah travels to California for her sister's wedding, she hears a rumor that her family was the real-life inspiration for "The Graduate."
Siddharth falls in love with beautiful Jhanvi. But Jhanvi's brother Ganpat is overly possessive – and determined to destroy their relationship.
Sparks fly when a newspaper columnist writes a one-sided, sexist story about a commitment-phobic bride who abandoned three men at the altar.
Held hostage by men searching for a secret her late husband left behind, a recent widow and her family race against time to find a way out.
A spunky terrier named Russell with serious wrestling chops becomes a sports phenomenon with the help of his coach, a monkey named Hunk.
Global comedy star Russell Peters leaves no ethnic or cultural stereotype unsatirized in this outrageous standup appearance in Sydney, Australia.
A decorated naval officer kills his wife's lover, leading to a sensational trial and a national obsession over passion versus premeditated murder.
This film examines the complex life of iconic filmmaker Stanley Kubrick, as seen through the eyes of his devoted longtime driver, Emilio D'Alessandro.
A veteran cop is tasked with drafting and training a special weapons and tactics team, who soon find themselves up against an international criminal.
A young woman falls for her classmate’s idealistic, non-materialistic ways, but is troubled upon seeing his principles change after they marry.
Italian filmmaker Gianfranco Rosi turns his eye to his own country, roaming and filming for over two years in a minivan on Rome's giant ring road.
An ex-boxer falls in love with a blind woman and starts to build a new life, but his violent past returns to endanger them both.
High schooler Sadie Mitchell believes the world is about to end – literally. Before it does, she sets out to kiss a boy and win back her best friend.
After a traumatic injury leaves her with amnesia and age regression, a young woman is sold to a brothel before a teacher becomes her savior.
This documentary profiles the celebrated Hindi film director known as much for his embrace of leftist politics and social concerns as lyrical cinema.
A charming cabbie, a cop turned assassin and a housewife who’s also a hooker share one thing in common: a bizarre and violent afternoon in Kolkata.
When two college students – a rich man’s daughter and a fisherman’s son – defy social edicts by falling in love, violence erupts in their village.
Caught in a downward spiral of failed career moves, misguided ambitions and bad relations, a pair of lost souls find hope in an unexpected friendship.
A street vendor's simple life is turned upside down after the Egyptian revolution of 2011, forcing him to contend with criminals and cops alike.
When a young girl is killed in a suspicious train accident, three very different lives become intertwined in their quest for answers.
Disliked for his stinginess, Samir finds his life turned upside down when he receives a windfall and launches a television channel.
The Biblical story of Samson becomes this sword-and-sandals epic about an Israelite warrior whose God-given brawn is undone by a beautiful temptress.
The king’s ship has been taken over by seemingly fearless pirates! Can Bheem find the one thing that might scare them away?
After the Allies invade Italy, the Liri Valley town of San Pietro becomes an example of the brutal effects of combat, both for soldiers and civilians.

In an effort to honor the family matriarch's dying wish, Urmila and her husband, Shrikant, embark on a quest to find a husband for charismatic yet choosey Sai. But some things are easier said than done.
Returning home from war after being assumed dead, a pilot weds the woman he has long loved, unaware that she had been planning to marry his best friend.
When a gift sack full of kittens gives Santa a bad allergic reaction, the kitties have to take over and deliver the presents on time.
Young orphan Nicolas learns how to guide a sleigh, slide down chimneys and other duties he'll need when he becomes the next Santa Claus.
When a palatial wedding venue turns out to be haunted, one of the families hosting the wedding hires a fearless Sikh to deal with the ghost.
A simple farmer's life becomes complicated after he resolves to save his village from an economic crisis by traveling to Australia to earn money.

Raised in working-class Mumbai, Manisha has an independent spirit that angers her father, who favors Manisha's medical student sister, Mini. Things reach a breaking point when Manisha's father beats her for accepting a modeling contract.
In the course of a human trafficking investigation, a conservative cop crosses paths with an artist-activist in a clash of worldviews.
Based on true events, this moving story centers on a Punjabi family whose celebration of their faith endures in the face of conflicting attitudes.
An aging blues guitarist and a grad student form an unlikely duo while busking on the street corners of 1980s Harlem.
Friends in their last year of college contemplate the future of their band as they juggle questions of love, work, family and identity.
The eldest of seven brothers who run a family farm together marries a pretty nurse, inspiring his country-bumpkin siblings to follow his example.
A teen struggling with gender identity and family tensions seeks hope and support in New York City's underground LGBTQ ballroom community.
A former professional boxer serving time in a brutal labor camp must fight incredible odds to gain his freedom and avenge an act of violence.
Desperate to support his son, a single father uses his talent with makeup to dress up as a woman to try out for a part in a commercial.
Desperately clinging to her youth, 28-year-old Megan tells her boyfriend she's attending a career seminar but hangs out with a teenage friend instead.
A seemingly ordinary girl learns she will turn into a mermaid on her 12th birthday and be forced to leave her life on land behind.
When a marshal moves back to his hometown, he finds a woman renting his property who refuses to leave but soon captures his affection.
The Wayans brothers spoof some of Hollywood's biggest blockbusters, including Scream, I Know What You Did Last Summer, The Matrix and American Pie.
Oskar Schindler becomes an unlikely humanitarian, spending his entire fortune to help save 1,100 Jews from Auschwitz during World War II.
When Daphne's TV show does a segment on real monsters, the gang fires up the Mystery Machine and heads to Moonscar Island, where zombies await.
Gale has written a best-seller which has been turned into a film. As the movie premiere looms closer, the mysterious deaths begin again.
This installment of the tongue-in-cheek horror franchise finds Sidney Prescott once again battling a crazed killer – this time, on a movie set.

Titulo: Seal Team Six: The Raid on Osama Bin Laden
Enredo: In this dramatic recreation, U.S. Navy SEAL Team 6 trains for a critical mission, then executes a tough nighttime raid on Osama Bin Laden's compound.
Decades after Detroit singer-songwriter Rodriguez disappeared following the commercial failure of his albums, two fans try to track down their idol.
A group of weary warriors transport a suspected witch believed to be responsible for spreading the devastating Black Plague.
Enchanted by a pretty pianist and the haunting melody she plays, a musical prodigy falls in love. But a secret soon threatens to derail their romance.
A former FBI investigator reopens the haunting 13-year-old murder case of his colleague, only to uncover shocking truths hidden since then.
Princess Diana's brother, Charles, the ninth Earl Spencer, leads a tour of Althorp House, the manor the Spencer family has called home for 500 years.
Tales of tragedy and scandal unfold through the history of Chatsworth, a grand estate that has been home to some of England's most noted aristocrats.

Titulo: Secrets of Henry VIII's Palace: Hampton Court
Enredo: The history of this grand 500-year-old palace is inextricably tied to the lavish lifestyle of King Henry VIII and the doomed fates of his six wives.

Titulo: Secrets of Her Majesty's Secret Service
Enredo: This documentary spotlights more than 100 years of operatives and operations in the U.K.'s secret service, the world's oldest intelligence agency.
Known as the setting of "Downton Abbey," Highclere Castle truly was the home of aristocrats and an army of servants, with a rich past to share.
Revisit famous cases and explore the history of Scotland Yard, one of the world's oldest detective forces and a name synonymous with crime solving.
American Harry Gordon Selfridge introduced Londoners to a new retail model that made shopping less of a practical pursuit and more of an adventure.

Titulo: Secrets of the Tower of London
Enredo: Explore the storied history of the iconic Tower of London as it evolved from a royal castle into a dungeon prison and, finally, an armory and mint.
Experts examine the ruins and relics hidden beneath London's surface, unearthing a Roman amphitheater, plague pits, air raid shelters and more.
Take an insider's tour of Parliament, Big Ben and Westminster Abbey to discover the little-known history and pageantry of these famous buildings.
Desperate for cash, klutzy private investigator Tekin searches for a wealthy woman's missing girl but faces one surprise and mishap after another.
This fast-paced documentary profiles Ayrton Senna, one of the greatest drivers in the history of Formula One racing, and a hero in his native Brazil.
After a terrorist attack in Guatemala, a baby is rendered deaf and motherless and her father is left to raise her alone.
A diamond heist goes horribly wrong, and the group of friends who sought to make a fortune must instead fight for their very survival.
Best friends Carrie, Miranda, Samantha and Charlotte take a break from their busy New York lives for an all-expenses-paid luxury vacation to Abu Dhabi.

Titulo: Sex and the City: The Movie
Enredo: When Carrie's big step forward in her relationship goes awry, best friends Charlotte, Miranda and Samantha are there to help her pick up the pieces.
A high-end call girl falls for a handsome man she meets at a nightclub, but he harbors a secret that throws a wrench in their relationship.
Passions flare and alliances form when neighbors Ana and Miguel each start an affair with former lovers, right under their spouses' noses.
A homeless vet who has PTSD steals a motorcycle and hits the road, trying to sort out what life means now that war is in the rear-view mirror.
At large in the city, five inmates of a mental asylum run up against the insanity of the outside world while trying to prevent a terrorist plot.
A young mother must break free of the clutches of her husband's feudal family and bring herself and her young child to safety.
Three disparate characters uncover government corruption as a small Indian town receives an influx of foreign money to turn it into the next Shanghai.
Unable to bribe his way out of a reckless driving charge, an arrogant rich kid is sentenced to community service at a home for senior citizens.
A weekend of beach-house debauchery turns into a nightmare for a group of friends when they discover that the waters are infested with vicious sharks.

Titulo: Shaurya: It Takes Courage to Make Right... Right
Enredo: Courtroom intrigue plays out against a backdrop of military secrets in this Bollywood drama with a plot that's reminiscent of A Few Good Men.
Go inside the lives of extraordinary, black female entrepreneurs as they discuss building legacies and pioneering a new future for the next generation.
A forensic psychiatrist has to think outside the box when she takes on a patient whose multiple personalities lead to a trail of murder victims.
The game is afoot for an eccentric detective who must use his brains and brawn to track down a nefarious nemesis with the help of his partner.
A young man enrolls at a college and becomes a rival to the student-union president, who’s using force and intimidation to advance his criminal agenda.
In this first full Shopkins movie, Peppa-Mint is the new Shoppie in town who stirs things up by hosting a team cooking competition.
Beloved movie star Scarletta Gateau visits Shopville and recruits the Shopkins for a quest through the jungle to the mysterious world of Pawville.
The Shopkins and Shoppies jet around the world in search of missing friend Kooky Cookie, a stolen diamond and more vloggable adventure.
A Hindu boy's feelings for a Muslim girl expose the tensions between their two communities and open the door to chaos and violence.
A new charge at a foster care facility dredges up the memories of a young supervisor's own troubled past, and her tough exterior begins eroding.
Chaos erupts when locals learn that an 11-year-old boy has discovered a mysterious rock that grants the wishes of whoever possesses it.

Titulo: SHOT! The Psycho-Spiritual Mantra of Rock
Enredo: Aptly named iconic rock photographer Mick Rock reconstructs his journey through the thrilling and murky universe of rock 'n' roll history.
An American woman on a revenge mission travels to India and befriends two journalists seeking justice for violent crimes against women.
When officials are slow to investigate a mysterious disappearance, a teen girl searches the dark woods on the outskirts of town for the boy she loves.
A principled mathematics teacher is shocked to discover that his grandson used unethical means to achieve academic success.
When a drug lord kidnaps his girlfriend’s daughter, a retired assassin leaves his newly peaceful life to go on a ruthless rampage to rescue the child.
Haunted by nightmares and her father's disappearance, Heather goes on the hunt for him – and discovers a disturbing truth about her own identity.
This documentary tells the story of Compaq Computer and its three founders, who in 1982, took on Goliath IBM at the height of its PC dominance.
As the result of a TV journalist's curiosity, the amazing saga of an honorable government tax collector's past comes to light.
Unemployed and immature, a somewhat pathetic bachelor sets his sights on finding a date for the wedding of his younger, more successful brother.
Nearly a century after artificial intelligence tried to eradicate people from Earth, two survivors search for a human enclave rumored to still exist.
A psychologist and her mute son confront evil forces at the site of a terrible tragedy involving an ancestral Ouija board and a demonic secret society.
A groom-to-be and his pals celebrate with a debauched night out that ends with a supernatural assault by a stripper who is not what she appears to be.
After the death of their beloved mother, three foster sisters find their bond tested by old grudges, career tensions and a startling revelation.
A New Jersey detective whose family was killed by an international gangster teams up with a Bangkok cop on a quest to bring down a criminal empire.
To capture a crime lord who killed his partner and kidnapped his partner's daughter, a Hong Kong detective teams with a smart aleck American gambler.
The security chief at a top-level medical facility must fight to ensure that revolutionary cancer research doesn't fall into the wrong hands.
Only a few women pilots take part in the sport of aerobatics. Director Fredric Lean captures their powerful spirit at the World Aerobatic Championships.
After a wild night of partying, Terry discovers that he's one of the few people left on Earth, then sets out to solve the mystery of what happened.
Many years after hooking up in college, two people cross paths and realize they are both serial philanderers who need each other's help to reform.
As high school approaches, four best friends have a summer sleepover and participate in a scavenger hunt against their popular archrivals.
A man returns home after being released from a psychiatric hospital, where he'd been confined since age 12 for murdering his mother and her lover.
A divorcée moves into a high-rise with a sordid past and begins a steamy affair with her neighbor, unaware that her every move is being monitored.
Determined to find the woman he loves, a Scottish teenager braves the Western frontier of 19th-century America, with bounty hunters hot on his trail.
An unexpected romance and a surprise visit from his wild brother turn the life of widowed professor Lawrence Wetherhold upside down.
Buckle up for a look inside a biannual school bus race in Florida, a harrowing event where carnage and collisions are most definitely encouraged.
To keep his teen crush from spotting him in an embarrassing YouTube video, Anthony and his friend Ian must enter the virtual world and alter the clip.
An arranged marriage becomes a friendship for Viren and Aditi, who aren't in love – until they begin having unexpected feelings for each other.
This biographical drama about Indonesia's first president recounts his nationalist crusade to seize independence from Dutch colonial rule.
A yuppie playboy looks for a quick death after being falsely diagnosed with AIDS by a nurse who was once cheated by the young Casanova.

Titulo: Solo: A Star Wars Story (Spanish Version)
Enredo: A young Han Solo tries to settle an old score with the help of his new buddy Chewbacca, a crew of space smugglers and a cunning old friend.
In this epic tale, a once-murderous sea captain is holed up in a monastery in retreat from the devil, whom the captain fears is coming for his soul.
A one-eyed boy and plus-sized girl form a deep connection. But following a brief separation, they reunite as different people.
A young petty thief who received protection from a notorious inmate in jail is forced to spring his defender from prison and help pull off a heist.
Passion is an understatement. Meet the folks who wanted a Major League Soccer club in Philadelphia so badly, they became fans before it even existed.
Hawaiian teen Bethany Hamilton bravely returns to competitive surfing after losing her left arm in a vicious shark attack.
Two siblings invite friends to their inherited, remote country home, but the fun stops when the group summons a demonic force from an old spellbook.
A dizzying chronicle of excess and deception dissects a fascinating case of fine-wine fraud and the con man who cheated investors out of millions.
In 1950s Harlem, three singing sisters hit the big time and end up losing one another in this musical melodrama inspired by the Supremes.
Fed up with the hypocrisy of the adults around them, three creative high school misfits revive an old debate club as a way to fight back.
This daredevil documentary trails behind and into the minds of the biggest names in one of the world's most dangerous sports, superbike racing.
The seemingly invincible Spider-Man goes up against an all-new crop of villains in the third installment of the blockbuster adventure series.
After being bitten by a radioactive spider, Brooklyn teen Miles Morales gets a crash course in web-slinging from his alternate-dimension counterparts.

Titulo: Spitfire: The Plane that Saved the World
Enredo: In this epic documentary, last-surviving veterans trace the history of a legendary fighter aircraft that dominated the air during the Battle of Britain.
A team of reporters and editors at the Boston Globe relentlessly investigate a shocking child molestation cover-up by the Catholic Church.
Four cash-strapped college women run afoul of the law — and fall in with a shady hustler — as they join the annual rite of bikinis, beer and debauchery.
When a Jamaican teen hopes to use track to reunite him with his mother in America, family dysfunction at home threatens to knock his plans off course.
The tables are turned when pint-sized kids Carmen and Juni must rescue their secret-agent parents from the diabolical clutches of Alexander Minion.

Titulo: Spy Kids 2: The Island of Lost Dreams
Enredo: Spy kids Carmen and Juni Cortez team up with two other pint-size secret agents, Gary and Gerti Giggles, in order to take on an evil scientist.
Carmen gets caught in a virtual reality game designed by the kids' new nemesis, the Toymaker, and it's up to Juni to save her by beating the game.
When his girlfriend dumps him for being a bore, a working stiff discovers that his father is a secret agent and a dangerous thug is targeting them.
Unwed and pregnant, a young woman flees her abusive home in 1950s Georgia and takes refuge at a mysterious convent with a terrible secret.
After a popular morning television host bumps into an old acquaintance with a dark past, her professional and personal lives begin to unravel.
After witnessing an assassin's slaughter, a young girl holes up in a farmhouse with a suicidal vet, who must use wits and guts to fend off the killer.
Four astronomers from England celebrate 50 years of friendship and achievement by taking a reflective road trip through the American Southwest.

Titulo: Star Wars: Episode VIII: The Last Jedi
Enredo: As the remnants of the Resistance flee Kylo Ren and the First Order, Rey seeks out Luke Skywalker – but he wants nothing more to do with the Force.
A British juvenile offender's violent temper gets him transferred to an adult prison, where he encounters his estranged father.
Journalists expose how smugglers, dealers, collectors and scholars promote plunder of ancient artifacts from war-torn Iraq, Afghanistan and Pakistan.
Brennan and Dale might be grown men, but that doesn't stop a childish sibling rivalry from erupting after Brennan's mom marries Dale's dad.
A down-on-his-luck man reads a book, only to have its characters materialize and take over his life.
In post-Partition Kolkata, a young Bengali poet from an urban colony wanders the city in search of the woman he loves and a channel for his sorrows.
After noting a strange odor in his child’s pajamas, a single dad’s search for the source uncovers potentially toxic secrets of the chemical industry.
In 1899, a young doctor arrives at an asylum for an apprenticeship and becomes suspicious of his mentor's methods while falling for a female patient.
When an astrologer gives him one year to find a mate or face being alone forever, a professor sets out to find a bride despite serious obstacles.
When a gay brainiac with OCD questions his identity, he enters a romantic relationship with a woman, leaving sex and physical intimacy out of it.
A young woman rattles her former boyfriend’s family when she reveals she is pregnant with his child — despite his death five years ago.
As a writer ponders how to kill off her main character, the man begins hearing her voice in his head and realizes that his days are numbered.
Dumped by his partner just before a major dance competition, gifted hoofer Scott Hastings is forced to take a graceless neophyte as his new partner.
A quarter-century later, this documentary relocates the male dancers who backed Madonna on her 1990 Blond Ambition tour, as seen in "Truth or Dare."
After losing everything, an indolent sad sack impulsively joins the U.S. Army and cajoles his best friend into enlisting, too.
A former FBI employee works as a stripper to finance her custody battle for her daughter when a secretly shady congressman takes an interest in her.
After a tough upbringing, natural-born fighter José Aldo confronts his personal demons in his quest to become an MMA champion in this sports biopic.
Zany misadventures are in store as lovable city mouse Stuart and his human brother, George, raise the roof in this sequel to the 1999 blockbuster.
After a near-death trip home, a Marine looking to help his comrade survive returns to the underground world of MMA, where new battles await.
A grueling battle over turning a seaside town near Rome into a gambling paradise exposes criminal rivalries and endemic corruption on a grand scale.
When his boyhood crush Ern returns, Ped forms a band with his friend to impress her. Romantic rivalries bloom after the talented Ern joins the group.
A failed businessman must kill himself to pay off a loan shark or his family will die, but a detective discovers the case turns on a shocking secret.
Waiting for news of her prisoner-of-war husband, a French woman in Nazi-occupied France reluctantly falls for a German officer quartering in her home.
When a quirk of fate kicks the Danish national soccer team into the European Championship final, the coach must whip his unprepared squad into shape.
While investigating a child kidnapping, a Mumbai police inspector is haunted by a shadowy dream figure and memories of his own abducted daughter.
Hoping to find a magical root, a monster has captured farmers in the land of Vyom. It’s up to Bheem and the gang to foil his plan and save the kingdom!
A loving, concerned American grandson travels to Mumbai to rescue his unappreciated grandmother from her drudgery and fulfill her true potential.
To get away from the thug life, cocaine dealer Youngblood Priest puts together one last deal that will net him enough money to start over.
When Superman returns to Metropolis, he finds that Lois Lane has moved on to another man and Lex Luthor is developing a new plan to rule the world.
A socially awkward Catholic schoolgirl vows to win a dreamy classmate’s affections by taking first prize at an upcoming talent show.
Hoping to fulfill her deceased mother's final wish, a young woman travels to Prague to deliver an old letter to a mysterious man.
Former inmates, officers and celebrities critique the U.S. prison system in this documentary packaged as a how-to handbook for the incarcerated.
Beyond her larger-than-life persona, this documentary reveals the woman behind the famed event planner, and her legacy as a cultural icon and activist.
Chef Rick Bayless, farmers and others discuss the history leading to the sustainable food movement and how it could change what we eat in the future.
After she enters into an arranged marriage, a spirited and intellectual young woman tries to adjust to life with a man who was not her choice.
A washed-up corpse with surprising abilities gives a hopeless man stranded in the wilderness someone to talk to – and a newfound reason to live.
Haunted by the past, a master swordsman masks his identity to work anonymously as a janitor in a brothel, setting in motion a violent chain of events.

Titulo: Sword Masters: Two Champions of Shaolin
Enredo: Shaolin warrior Tung Chien-chen is injured in battle against the hated Wu Tang clan, and nursed back to health by a knife-throwing master. As he recovers, Tung learns this deadly art, and also falls in love with his teacher's daughter.
Businessman Manav falls for aspiring singer Mansi, but their romance faces an uphill climb when Manav must depart and Mansi's suave manager moves in.
After his family's donkey is confiscated by a moneylender, 8-year-old Tahaan travels across conflict-torn Kashmir to find his beloved pet.
Set in the financial boom of the late 1980s, this tale centers on a recent college grad trying to figure out what to do with his life.
A man and a woman on the run from the law are drawn to each other through the common bond of their mutual dependency.
A night out in Paris quickly unravels when two friends provoke the wrong taxi driver, who's after something bigger than cab fare.
After being shipwrecked off the African coast, a lone child grows up in the wild, and is destined to become lord of the jungle.
How did the King of the Jungle ascend to the throne? Find out in this charming prequel to the hit animated movie that catches Tarzan as a young child.
A down-on-his-luck man must prove he's not as hapless as he seems when the woman he's on a date with is suddenly kidnapped.

Titulo: Tayo the Little Bus Movie: Mission Ace
Enredo: After he loses his favorite racing car, Duri ventures to a mysterious, magical land filled with toys that have been thrown away.
It's been decades since Brown v. Board of Education, yet American schools remain largely segregated. Some leaders are working to change that.

Luck brings together math expert Perci Trachtenberg and obscure genius Venkat Subramaniam in a casino, but the foundations of probability may be utterly altered when their chat leads Subramaniam to try a new theory in the gambling dens of Mumbai.
Two teen girls form an intense bond and launch a lucrative webcam business, leading them to a dangerous encounter with a middle-aged married man.
In this animated adventure, Master Splinter whips the four Ninja Turtles back into shape to defeat monsters running amok in New York.

Titulo: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles II: The Secret of the Ooze
Enredo: The evil Shredder decides that ooze is what gives the ninja turtles their power, so he obtains some of the toxic junk and creates dangerous mutants.

Titulo: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles: The Movie
Enredo: After exposure to a strange, glowing ooze, four mutant turtles train as ninjas in the sewers and fight crime wherever they find it.
A flamboyant con artist and his band of gleeful robbers gamble with fate when smugglers hire them to swipe antiques from a speeding train.
Three teenaged best friends on the planet Telluria begin an incredible journey of adventure as they fight against the most evil being in the universe.
Animosity gives way to love and forgiveness when an angry teenager reunites with his estranged biological father in the wilds of Patagonia.
Ten years after John Connor saved Earth from Judgment Day, he encounters T-X, a robotic assassin ordered to finish what T-1000 started.
All grown up in post-apocalyptic 2018, John Connor must lead the resistance of humans against increasingly dominating militaristic robots.
This visually arresting documentary essay reflects on our relationship to other living creatures as humanity becomes more isolated from nature.
On Halloween night, inside a dilapidated apartment building, Art the Clown stalks his victims, slicing and slaughtering in terrifying silence.
New beginnings appear to be on the horizon after a simple country boy forms a bond with a sophisticated urban girl with modern ideas.
This high-octane thriller tells the story of a man on a mission to reclaim what was taken from him and the agent who's determined to stop him.
An intense rivalry between Henry Ford II of the Ford Motor Company and Enzo Ferrari results in the most epic showdown in racing history.
In a violent prison in 1970s Mexico, a young inmate lands a spot on a football team that doubles as an enforcer squad for a corrupt administration.
Decades after WWII, a former SS officer stands trial in his native Germany after being charged for his complicity in the murder of Jews at Auschwitz.
Author Stephen Elliott has a problem separating his own life from incidents in the life of a convicted murderer about whom he's writing a book.
After finding a peculiar key, three smart and adventurous kids launch a quest to uncover the whereabouts of a coveted archaeological treasure.

Titulo: The Adventures of Sharkboy and Lavagirl
Enredo: A 10-year-old dreamer's imaginary friends – mighty Sharkboy and fire-producing Lavagirl – come to life to seek his help battling a nefarious baddie.

In the City Without a Voice, only faceless singer the Voice can still vocalize. Everyone else has lost the power of speech as they let Mr. TV's broadcasts speak for them. But when Mr. TV kidnaps the Voice, things change.
Formerly a Korean resistance fighter, a policeman working for Japan is tasked with tracking down resistance leaders before they acquire explosives.
The widowed president strikes up a romance with a beautiful Washington lobbyist – but can the couple keep their private and political lives separate?
This hair-raising remake of the 1979 horror hit depicts the ordeal of the Lutz family, whose new home has a gory past and a legacy of demons.
Animal rights protesters trying to shut down a facility that conducts animal testing are labeled terrorists by big business and law enforcement.
Released after being wrongly imprisoned in Iraq, an Egyptian contractor returns home to a country on the brink of revolution.
A young man determined to renounce Catholicism by having his baptismal records excised is thwarted by church bureaucracy and his own inner conflicts.
Crunch Calhoun, a daredevil motorcyclist and mostly reformed con artist, agrees to do one last job: helping his brother Nicky steal a priceless book.
Framed for the murder of an ambassador, a former member of the United Nations' elite covert action unit will do whatever it takes to clear his name.
A hitman has his body surgically altered into a woman's against his will. Now he has to track down the surgeon responsible and get his revenge.
A father-son team of small-town coroners performs an autopsy on an unidentified woman with mysterious injuries and a terrifying secret.

Britain's most ineffective but caring teacher takes his class to Cornwall for one last school trip, where anything could happen –
 and probably will.
In this documentary, teachers at a Mojave Desert high school adhere to a belief that compassion and life skills can profoundly help at-risk students.
Known for tortuous role-play with victims in his basement, a twisted serial killer abducts a musician who has a deeper connection to his mind games.
Director John Ford captures combat footage of the Battle of Midway, an air and sea campaign that was a turning point in the war in the Pacific.

Titulo: The Bill Murray Stories: Life Lessons Learned From a Mythical Man
Enredo: This documentary highlights spontaneous encounters with the elusive, comedic veteran, who touches lives by simply showing up anywhere.
A couple's new dream home morphs into a nightmare after they learn that an evil and lustful spirit resides in their basement.
When their parents fail to pick them up for winter break, two students stay on at an all-girls boarding school in the company of a terrible presence.
Husband. Father. Fighter. Meet Chuck Wepner, the liquor salesman and self-proclaimed real-life inspiration behind Rocky Balboa.
Form, montage and mesmerizing kinetics propel this experimental meditation on the destructive power of the nuclear bomb, featuring music by The Acid.
Determined to protect a sacred text that promises to save humanity, Eli goes on a quest westward across the barren, postapocalyptic country.
While working together, a married textile foreman and his boss’s daughter have a torrid love affair, stirring up hostility among the factory crew.
Bounty hunter Milo Boyd finds his latest assignment downright satisfying as he learns that the bail-jumper he must chase down is his ex-wife, Nicole.
A couple must decide whether to push a button that will net them a million dollars but that will also cause the death of a complete stranger.
A nanny is hired by a couple to look after their boy. She's shocked to learn that her charge is actually a doll that the couple treats like a human.

Titulo: The Boy in the Striped Pajamas
Enredo: When his family moves from Berlin to Poland, a young boy befriends a boy who lives on the other side of the fence, unaware he's a Jewish prisoner.
New York City radio host Erica Bain decides to take the law into her own hands after losing her fiancé in a brutal Central Park attack.
Newly famous after challenging Muhammad Ali for a championship title, boxer Chuck Wepner spirals down the slippery slope of being a celebrity.
A courageous 11-year-old Afghan girl disguises herself as a boy and takes on odd jobs to provide for her family when her father is arrested.
Cohabitating couple Gary and Brooke's petty spats turn into an all-out battle for their home condo.
A Yoruba prince and a young lady from a prominent Igbo family face tribal prejudice and parental pressure when they secretly wed.
Brothers Jake and Will Grimm travel from village to village, posing as exterminators of magical creatures. But in reality, they're expert con artists.
Two terminally ill men bust out of the cancer ward with a plan to experience life to the fullest before they kick the bucket.
A taxi driver longs to be a pop singer, but the road to stardom is wrought with competition and struggle until he befriends a helpful belly dancer.
After losing everything, a young man rebuilds his life and finds love in 1920s Shanghai – all while rising to power in an organized crime syndicate.
Three college students move into an off-campus house and discover they've unwittingly unleashed a supernatural killer known as the Bye Bye Man.
His way of life under threat due to the oil fracking boom, a young rancher defends a Lakota woman and becomes entangled in human trafficking.
When a German baker travels to Jerusalem in search of his dead male lover’s family, his growing involvement with them may expose his truth.
Eight years after their daughter's abduction tore them apart, her parents receive enigmatic clues from the kidnapper hinting that she's still alive.
In his small Southwestern town, sheriff Wade Parent must find out who — or what — is running people down via a mysterious, driverless black sedan.
Featuring eight-time NBA All-Star Vince Carter, this documentary takes an in-depth look at his impact on pop culture and the Canadian basketball scene.
Bothered by his wife's unyielding belief in Christianity, an investigative reporter sets out to use verifiable facts to poke holes in her faith.
A special operations officer vows to get revenge against the terrorist who killed his friend in a brutal attack.
After an architect transforms a slaughterhouse into trendy lofts, its new inhabitants discover that the structure is haunted by its evil past.
A detective investigates the murder of a young musician, whose philandering lifestyle leaves a long list of suspects and a lot of questions.
In 1937, Spanish revolutionary Ramón trains as a Soviet spy, impersonating a wealthy Belgian as part of a plot to assassinate Leon Trotsky in Mexico.
Young Ulises falls in love with teen Sofia, even as he is forced to lure her into his family's prostitution ring. Now he'll do anything to rescue her.
Four brothers prepare for war when they're forced to deliver secret holiday gifts to the school bullies. But they soon learn kindness goes a long way.

In Depression-era New Orleans, cocksure stud poker player Eric Stoner – the titular Cincinnati Kid – challenges longtime champ Lancey "The Man" Howard to a showdown at the table, where a war of wills – and nerve – ensues.
